Pre-Game Insights: Malta aims to win promotion in the UEFA Nations League under coach Michele Marcolini.
Moldova's strong performance in Euro 2024 qualifying, including a victory against Poland, indicates their strength.
Moldova will play in front of home fans, adding a challenge for Malta.
Malta faces three injured players: Steve Borg, Enrico Pepe, and Bjorn Kristensen.
Malta's goal is to win the group and gain promotion to League C.
